snippet.title: NEC PC-FX Homebrew : Simple Battle FX
snippet.description:
Here's my first homebrew for PCFX.
It's a RPG but with only battles and is similar to one of my previous project called RPG DOS. 
(also known as Sonyc Rpg Console)

And NO, it has no porn.
The very first playable homebrew game for PCFX is Soviet Union 2010.
(Although it had a rather confidential release and was programmed entierely in assembly)

Download link :
https://github.com/gameblabla/simplebattlefx-pcfx/raw/master/release/SimpleBattle_FX.zip
